[" <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: -52.65pt\" dir=\"rtl\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"30\">\n   إِذَا عَاشَ امْرُؤٌ سِتِّينَ عَاماً</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"30\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"30\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n فَنِصْفُ الْعُمْرِ تَمْحَقُهُ اللَّيَالِي</td>\n  </tr>\n <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"33\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">وَ \n نِصْفُ النِّصْفِ يَذْهّبْ لَيْسَ يَدْرِي</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"33\">\n   &nbsp;</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"33\">\n   لِغَفْلَتِهِ يَمِيناً عَنْ شِمَالٍ</td>\n  </tr>\n <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"34\">\n   وَ ثُلْثُ النِّصْفِ آمَالٌ وَ حِرْصٌ</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"34\">\n   &nbsp;</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"34\">\n   &nbsp;وَ شُغْلٌ بِالْمَكَاسِبِ وَ الْعِيَالِ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"35\">\n   وَ بَاقِي الْعُمْرِ أَسْقَامٌ وَ شَيْبٌ </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"35\">\n   &nbsp;</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"35\">\n   وَ هَمٌّ بِارْتِحَالٍ وَ انْتِقَالٍ‏</td>\n  </tr>\n <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   فَحُبُّ الْمَرْءِ طُولَ الْعُمْرِ جَهْلٌ </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   &nbsp;</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   وَ قِسْمَتُهُ عَلَى هَذَا الْمِثَال‏</td>\n  </tr>\n  </table>","ديوان الإمام علي(ع)"]